snippet.title: Full Song List | Just Dance 2022 [Official]
snippet.description:
Just Dance 2022 is available tomorrow! Get ready to hit the dance floor to 40 new, hot tracks!

Coming to Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, Xbox Series X, PS4, PS5 and Google Stadia!

#JustDance2022 #JustDance

Please SUBSCRIBE:
https://www.youtube.com/user/justdancegame

Follow Just Dance:
Website: https://justdance.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/justdancegame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/justdance.usa/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/justdancegame_us
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@justdance_officialgame

ABOUT JUST DANCE 2022:
Grab your friends and family because it's time to turn up the volume and let loose with Just Dance 2022! 

The #1 Music Video Game Franchise of All Time,  with over 77million units sold, is back this fall with 40 new  songs and universes, Just Dance will get you moving all year long!

Join a community of more than 138 million players around the world and dance it out!

About Ubisoft   

Ubisoft is a leading creator, publisher and distributor of interactive entertainment and services, with a rich portfolio of world-renowned brands, including Assassin’s Creed, Far Cry, For Honor, Just Dance, Watch Dogs, Tom Clancy’s video game series including Ghost Recon, Rainbow Six and The Division. The teams throughout Ubisoft’s worldwide network of studios and business offices are committed to delivering original and memorable gaming experiences across all popular platforms, including consoles, mobile phones, tablets and PCs. For the 2019-20 fiscal year, Ubisoft generated net bookings of €1,534 million. To learn more, please visit: www.ubisoftgroup.com. 
 
© 2021 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. Ubisoft and the Ubisoft logo are registered trademarks in the US and/or other countries.
